attr.title: No Transmission
attr.desc:
Parasites know  that the best place to infect people is at underground raves.
Don't kill (hang) the DJ or the obliviously high dancing civilians.... unless you have to. 
YCJY made this for a Global Game Jam - to experiment with 3d in gamemaker.
attr.inst:
Download the game from https://ycjy.itch.io/no-transmission
Extract the .exe from the zip and place it in notransmission/gamedata
On first startup, the game will patch!
